[[bench]]
name = "benchmarks"
harness = false

[package]
name = "flash-lso"
version = "0.6.0"
authors = [ "CUB3D <callumthom11@gmail.com>",]
description = "Fast and safe SOL/AMF0/AMF3 parsing. Supports serde, Adobe flex and cyclic references"
repository = "https://github.com/CUB3D/rust-sol"
readme = "README.md"
license = "MIT"
keywords = [ "sol", "amf", "parser", "serializer", "flash",]
edition = "2021"
categories = [ "data-structures", "encoding", "parser-implementations",]

[dependencies]
nom = "7.1.3"
cookie-factory = "0.3.2"
enumset = "1.0.12"
thiserror = "1.0.38"

[dev-dependencies]
pretty_assertions = "1.2.1"
serde_json = "1.0.91"
criterion = "0.5.1"

[features]
default = []
flex = []
serde = [ "dep:serde", "enumset/serde",]
all = [ "serde", "flex",]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.152"
optional = true
features = [ "derive", "rc",]

[package]
name = "h263-rs"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Mike Welsh <mwelsh@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2018"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"

[dependencies]
bitflags = "2.4.0"
thiserror = "1.0.47"
num-traits = "0.2.16"
lazy_static = "1.4.0"

[package]
name = "h263-rs-deblock"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "TÖRÖK Attila <torokati44@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2018"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"

[dependencies]
wide = "0.7.11"
itertools = "0.11.0"

[package]
name = "h263-rs-yuv"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Mike Welsh <mwelsh@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2018"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"

[dependencies]
wide = "0.7.11"
bytemuck = "1.13.1"

[package]
name = "jpegxr"
version = "0.3.1"
authors = [ "Brooke Vibber <bvibber@pobox.com>",]
edition = "2018"
license = "BSD-3-Clause"
description = "Wrapper for Microsoft's C JPEG XR image codec library"
readme = "readme.md"
homepage = "https://github.com/brion/jpegxr"
repository = "https://github.com/brion/jpegxr.git"
keywords = [ "jxr", "jpegxr", "jpeg-xr",]
categories = [ "multimedia::images",]

[dependencies]
thiserror = "1.0.57"
libc = "0.2.153"

[build-dependencies]
bindgen = "0.69.4"

[build-dependencies.cc]
version = "1.0.83"
features = [ "parallel",]

[package]
name = "nellymoser-rs"
version = "0.1.2"
authors = [ "relrelb <relrelbachar@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2021"
description = "A pure Rust decoder for the Nellymoser audio codec"
license = "MIT"

[dependencies]
bitstream-io = "2"
once_cell = "1.10.0"
rustdct = "0.7.0"

[package]
name = "nihav_duck"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Kostya Shishkov <kostya.shishkov@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2018"

[dependencies.nihav_core]
path = "../nihav-core"

[dependencies.nihav_codec_support]
path = "../nihav-codec-support"

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/ruffle-rs/rust-flash-lso"]
git = "https://github.com/ruffle-rs/rust-flash-lso"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "2f770555ea49c6db49c57c1dd46c7cc686e8dacc"

[source."https://github.com/ruffle-rs/h263-rs"]
git = "https://github.com/ruffle-rs/h263-rs"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "16700664e2b3334f0a930f99af86011aebee14cc"

[source."https://github.com/ruffle-rs/jpegxr"]
git = "https://github.com/ruffle-rs/jpegxr"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "ruffle"

[source."https://github.com/ruffle-rs/nellymoser"]
git = "https://github.com/ruffle-rs/nellymoser"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "754b1184037aa9952a907107284fb73897e26adc"

[source."https://github.com/ruffle-rs/nihav-vp6"]
git = "https://github.com/ruffle-rs/nihav-vp6"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "83c7e1094d603d9fc1212d39d99abb17f3a3226b"
